Class RaiseCancellationException

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Throwable
java.lang.Exception

java.util.concurrent.CancellationException
info.jab.util.raise.RaiseCancellationException
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
NoTrace, Traced
public sealed class RaiseCancellationException extends CancellationException permits Traced, NoTrace
This class represents a specific type of CancellationException that occurs when a raise operation is canceled.

It is a sealed class that permits only Traced and NoTrace subclasses.
